The zerk changes have gutted the class.  Sure, we can go 2handed and hit for big hits, but I never wanted big hits; I rarely hit for them.  But, I enjoyed having a chance against most classes, I lost as many as I won.  I enjoyed being able to go solo some yellow cons pretty easily to garner some coin, taking the place of a warrior as tank in a PvE group because I could deal more damage and still have decent defense.  We've lost all of that.  <br>
